20/07/23, 23:51 - Abir BHAI: আলাপন ও সুকল্যানের অমর প্রেম

আলাপন আর সুকল্যান, দুজন কপালে কপাল,
বন্ধুত্বের গহন মাঝে গড়ে মিলানো হোক সবার জন্য এই কাহিনীর কালপতরুর তলে।

স্বপ্নের মেলায় মিশে গিয়ে দুজন ছোঁয়া সমুদ্রে,
একটি অপরিসীম আবেগে মৃদুত্ব প্রদান করে।
সারা জীবন এই দুজন সাথে যাঁরা পালে,
ক্ষণেই আপন আর সুখের নাম মিশে যায় তাদের মনে।

প্রতিবাদ নেই, কেবল একই সঙ্গীর কাছে তাদের ভালবাসা,
আবার সমান্তরালে চলে যায় দুজনের সঙ্গ বিকাশা।
এই নিঃস্বার্থ প্রেমে ভরা মধুর এ কাহিনী,
জাগো বাংলা, গর্ব হউ আমি তাদের সত্যি ভালোবাসার জন্যি।

আলাপন ও সুকল্যানের অমর প্রেম,
প্রতিদিন তাদের বন্ধুত্বে মিশে যায় নতুন স্বপ্ন।
এই নির্মল ভালোবাসা যে দুজন করে,
হৃদয়ে বাজে নিত্য এক সুরে শুধু প্রেম।

আলাপন আর সুকল্যান, এই দুজন জীবনের দ্বন্দ্বে,
মিলিয়ে আছে দুজন সুন্দর প্রেমিক একসাথে।
এই দু'হারা প্রেমে আমরা সবাই উদাসীন,
কারণ তাদের ভালোবাসা তো একজনের সাথে আবার একজনের প্রতি মাত্র মিলে পাবে তা নয় সকলের সাথে।

আমরা ভালোবাসি এই দুজনকে,
তাদের প্রেমে ভরা এ কাহিনী আমাদের হৃদয় জুড়ে রাখে সবার জন্য।
সারা বাংলা ভাষায় গুঞ্জে আমাদের প্রেমের সুর,
আলাপন আর সুকল্যানের প্রেমে বন্ধুত্বের কাহিনী আমরা গাই সর্বজনীন ভাষায়।

আমাদের ভালোবাসা কখনো পরিস্থিতি অনুবর্তী,
আলাপন আর সুকল্যানের প্রেম অনন্ত, অমর আর অকাঙ্ক্ষী।
যেখানে প্রেমের আলো ছড়িয়ে দেয় সবার কাছে,
সেই স্থানে সবার মনে হোক আমরা আমরা এক সুন্দর প্রেমে বাধা করি না আমাদের কাছে।

20/09/23, 12:37 - Shreya Sen: Okay everyone, this post has been due since 2019. It's going to be long and graphic. TW of abuse.

I would love to say that I am doing this to help women, to spread awareness, etc other politically correct, acceptable reasons. But I am doing this out of hatred. Anger. Helplessness. To get rid of this weight I have been carrying for so many years. Just to drive a point that while you may cut out the abusers from your life, you will have a difficult time trying to rid yourself of their poison. Which is why you should be all the more careful who you become close to. 

This is dedicated to my beloved Raj Banerjee.

I met him in 2019, freshly out of a difficult breakup. Vulnerable. Emotionally Raw and ready to bond to the first person who shows me love. Trying to find a rebound on Tinder. Being young didn't necessarily help my situation. And Raj knew these things. He pretended to be exactly what I needed. He was charming. He fed all my fantasies of what a boyfriend should be.

His facade lasted all of 3 months. I moved to Mumbai to learn tattooing. And he showed me his true colours. Extremely insecure. Controlling. Misogynistic. I tried to breakup with him. He would not leave me alone. Not even when I told him that I'm interested in other guys in Mumbai. 

He is a master of emotional manipulation. When he noticed that I was trying to get rid of him, he started starving himself and doing drugs. Told me that it is because I "cheated on him" and he can't stop till I come back to him in Kolkata and we could start our life together again. So I did. 

He told me my parents sucked, they didn't deserve to have me in their home. I should fight with them the second I land in Kolkata, I should come to him the very same night and we should live together. He would hide me in his room, only his mother Patrali Banerjee  would know, and everything will be perfect again. So I came. I didn't even stay a single night in my own home after landing from Mumbai. I took my bags to his house and settled there. 

Within a week, the beatings began. The first time he really "beat" me, (to distinguish this from the causal slap here and there), his friend had come over and he had smacked my butt in front of a random guy I had never met before. He loved doing things like that. Showing me off. Of course I was angry. I had pushed him and hit his eye accidentally, and ran out. He called me back home. I reached and he was on his gaming chair. Playing. Ignoring me. I went to him to check up on his eye. He grabbed my hair (loved doing that, it was his favourite, always asked me to keep it long). He pushed me down to his feet. And kicked my face and head. Repeatedly. With the force with which one would kick a football. Again and again, for several minutes. Everytime I tried to get up, he kicked me back down. Several hours later, he had to wash me and keep me awake the rest of the night because he was afraid he might have given me a concussion and I might die in my sleep.

This followed 2 years of weekly beatings. Let me recap some highlights for you 😄

He loved to choke me with whatever objects he could find nearby. Sometimes some random dirty cloth , sometimes my own clothing, most of the times he would shove his whole fist down my throat and keep it there to keep me quiet in case his family heard. My mouth had cuts and sores for 2 years from this. 

While he choked me till I couldn't breath and started seeing black, he loved to tell me how it was my fault. How I "made him this way". How no man would ever be able to date me without losing his temper and beating me because that's the kind of girl I am. How I wanted him to beat me so that I could defame him later infront of everyone ( I barely told anyone, and when I did, it was for my own mental relief rather than his defamation).

Once, he shoved a broom down my throat. Yeah. You read it right. A broom. And he took off the plastick from the handle and stabbed my arms and legs with the backside of the broom, the staws cutting holes into my flesh. Those are pictures you see. Taken 3 days after the incident. He started in the morning, and he stopped in the evening. When he was done, the broomstick was completely broken into pieces. 

Once he ripped my clothes and forced me to use the washroom infront of him, while threatening and hitting me with an iron rod when I refused. You see, he was afraid I would lock myself in the washroom and poison myself with phenyl and then he and his mother would have to deal with a dead girl. Would've been an utter inconvenience. 

The amount of times he has beaten me are countless. The severity unimaginable to anyone reading this. Morning to evening, every week, over the stupidest issues you could imagine. The state of my body for the 2 years was that of a beaten and broken animal. 

His mother knew. She supported him. Protected him. So much so that one time when I was lying under him naked , bruised and broken he had the audacity to tell me that if I ran out in the street and accused him even in this state, nobody would believe me because they love him and his family in Girish Park. 

This person even had sex with me right after beating me in hopes that I would get confused and think he was being "rough" with me in bed. He tried to convince me of loving it because I was such a kinky girl after all. 

But the only thing this man couldn't touch was my self perception. No matter how hard he tried to convince me that this was my fault, he couldn't break me. I left Kolkata. I started a new life in a new city with new people. I had to run to save myself. 

Now let me move on to the rest of him. The greedy, lusty bits.

He learnt tattooing from me and used my equipment to start his "career". And I loved supporting him, standing by him. I had such admiration for his art. I was glad to help him. I have helped him to this day in his profession. One of the main reasons I had not come out with this was to protect his career. 

But let alone any credit or thanks, I don't think anybody is even aware of my role in his journey. Instead, him being a tattoo artist became a way for him to look cool infront of other women he would want to call to his house to fuck under the pretence of tattooing. 

Now let's move to money. He used mine. Thoroughly. Shamelessly. Continuously. He had no restraint, even when I told him that this was causing money troubles for  me and fights with my parents. All the dates, all the gifts, food, trips, would be paid by me for the major part whether I was ok with it or not. His and his Mother's grand plan was for me to convince my father to sponsor the opening of a tattoo studio for "us" eventually. 

I am ashamed of not taking action and foolishly believing that he has changed. For trusting and protecting and enabling in some part. There are a countless other things I could talk about here. Millions of ways in which this person is scum. But let me stop for now. Oindrila Dey has my full support in legal capacity and otherwise to put this person behind bars. 

And to anybody going through anything similar, this person's abuse has changed me as a human being. I am no longer kind. I am short tempered, pessimistic, quick to assume the worst about people. I enjoy cruelty to some extent now, because it gives me a sick sense of justice to see things suffer when I had to suffer this much.

I used to be kind, loving, trusting. This is the greatest loss I could've suffered and I am trying to heal from it. 

Thanks for reading till here, if you did.

21/09/23, 22:41 - Abir BHAI: A defining moment in our nation's democratic journey! Congratulations to 140 crore Indians. 

I thank all the Rajya Sabha MPs who voted for the Nari Shakti Vandan Adhiniyam. Such unanimous support is indeed gladdening. 

With the passage of the Nari Shakti Vandan Adhiniyam in Parliament, we usher in an era of stronger representation and empowerment for the women of India. This is not merely a legislation; it is a tribute to the countless women who have made our nation. India has been enriched by their resilience and contributions. 

As we celebrate today, we are reminded of the strength, courage, and indomitable spirit of all the women of our nation. This historic step is a commitment to ensuring their voices are heard even more effectively.

 মেরি, তোমার জীবনে এইতো প্রথম দুঃখ-কিন্তু আমার জীবন! কত জনকে হারিয়েছি, কত সহ্য করেছি!... স্বামীজি তারপর লিখেছেন মেরি তুমি আচ্ছাদনের তলায় কাটিয়েছে, আর আমি বাইরে দাঁড়িয়ে জ্বলেছি, পুড়েছি-দারিদ্র্যে,বিশ্বাসঘাতকতায় আর নিজের নির্বুদ্ধিতায়!"
 তবুও বিবেকানন্দ হাসেন।কারণ তিনি জানেন প্রকৃতিকে জয় করতেই হবে।এই দুঃখ প্রকৃতির দান। আবার চিঠিতে বলছেন ,"আমার প্রকৃতিতে পুরুষের চেয়ে মেয়েগুণ বেশি। আমি সবসময়ই অন্যের দুঃখ বেদনা শুধু শুধু নিজের উপর টেনে নিই,... ঠিক যেমন মেয়েদের সন্তান নাহলে একটা বিড়াল পুষে তার উপর ভালোবাসা ঢেলে দেয়।..পৃথিবীতে যদি কাউকে ভালবাসতে না হতো বেঁচে যেতাম!যদি বাল্যেই আত্মীয়হীন হয়ে অনাথ বালক হতাম! আমার আত্মীয়রাই আমাদের জীবনের সবচেয়ে বড় দুঃখের কারণ- আমার ভাই ,বোন, মা। আত্মীয়রা মানুষের গতির পক্ষে সবচেয়ে মারাত্মক বাধা। কী বিচিত্র! তবুও মানুষ বন্ধন বাড়াতে ছোটে বিয়ের দ্বারা!!"
প্রকৃতি বলবে কাঁদো আমরা তার নির্দেশ মেনে নিয়ে কাঁদতে শুরু করে দেবো, এতো আত্মশক্তির পরাজয়!তাই প্রকৃতিকে চ্যালেঞ্জ করে তিনি অদ্বৈত বাদী হয়ে প্রকৃতির মায়াকে ভস্মীভূত করেছেন তাঁর তৃতীয় নয়নে। তিনি শিবের অবতার, তাঁর তৃতীয় নয়ন জ্ঞানের আর অপর দুটি নয়ন প্রেমের। জাগতিক দুঃখকে বশীভূত করে তাই তিনি শেষ পর্যন্ত ত্রিনয়নে হাসিতে ঝলমল করে উঠেছেন। জয়তু স্বামীজি। সূত্র:সহাস্য বিবেকানন্দ;শংকরী প্রসাদ বসু।
প্রণাম  স্বামীজী।
সংগৃহীত।
